messages.content: The document is about a scene where characters Brahaspati and Shiva are discussing whether or not to accept an invitation from a place called Meluha. Brahaspati, who views Meluha positively due to its perceived fairness and prosperity, wants to go, while Shiva remains skeptical of the offer. [(Document Name: 35a6a966-b5ed-4c28-9406-4c6b4604cc97.txt, Page: 1)]
